btw, this is a MWE that behaves differently on the two versions:
```julia&gt; using GLM

julia&gt; x = [1.0 1.0
            1.0 2.0
            1.0 -1.0];

julia&gt; y = [1.0, 3.0, -2.0];

julia&gt; m = lm(x, y);

julia&gt; predict(m, x, interval=:confidence)```

elements.text:
julia> using GLM

julia> x = [1.0 1.0
            1.0 2.0
            1.0 -1.0];

julia> y = [1.0, 3.0, -2.0];

julia> m = lm(x, y);

julia> predict(m, x, interval=:confidence)
